block content

    //.hero-sky: .container: h1 2017 Fall League Registration

    .container.register: .row: .col-md-12
        
        img.beach-series-logo(src='/images/beach-ultimate-series-logo.jpg')

        p Greetings beach ultimate lovers!
        
        p South Florida Ultimate is happy to announce a series of beach ultimate hat tournaments coming in 2019!
        
        h3 Description
        p The series consists of 3 beach ultimate Frisbee hat tournaments held on the following three dates, each one starting at 10am sharp.

        ul
            li Saturday January 5, 2019
            li Saturday February 2nd, 2019 
            li Saturday March 2, 2019 

        p Register as an individual or as a pair. We'll make even teams and play a round robin!
        p Each event cost $20 per player. You can sign for each one individually or all 3 for $50. 
        p A portion of the proceeds will go to support the upcoming season of Fiasco Ultimate, South Florida's spicy women's team! 
        p There will also have discs and merch for sale.
        p Post game tournament party is across the street at Park and Ocean! 
        
        h3 Location
        p Games will be held the beach across from Hugh Taylor Birch State Park, 3109 E Sunrise Blvd. Ft Lauderdale, FL.
        p There is all day parking available in the park for $6 per vehicle.
        
        iframe(src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2595.3871114681165!2d-80.10347306511046!3d26.14049539386033!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x6f9406a6e78e90c1!2sPark+%26+Ocean!5e1!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1508698698564" width="100%" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen)

            
        h3 Registration

        form#registration(autocomplete="off")
            
            .row
                .col-md-6
                    .form-group
                        label(for='first_name') First Name
                        input#first_name.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='first_name' placeholder='' value=formData.firstName required)
                .col-md-6
                    .form-group
                        label(for='last_name') Last Name
                        input#last_name.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='last_name' placeholder='' value=formData.lastName required)
                        
            .form-group
                label(for='email') Email Address
                input#email.input-lg.form-control(type='email' name='email' placeholder='' value=formData.email required)
            
            .form-group
                label(for='partner_name') Partner Name
                input#partner_name.input-lg.form-control(type='text' name='partner_name' placeholder='' value=formData.email required)
            
            .form-group
                label(for="gender" name="gender") Gender
                select#gender.input-lg.form-control(name="gender" value=formData.gender)
                    option(value='Female') Female
                    option(value='Male') Male

            .form-group
                label Registration Dates
                
                .checkbox
                    label
                        input(type="checkbox" value="")
                        | Saturday January 5, 2019
                .checkbox
                    label
                        input(type="checkbox" value="")
                        | Saturday January 5, 2019
                .checkbox
                    label
                        input(type="checkbox" value="")
                        | Saturday March 2, 2019

            h3 Waiver

            .checkbox
                label
                    input(type='checkbox', value='' required)
                    | I agree to SFLUltimate's <a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#waiver">terms & conditions</a>.

            h3 Payment Information
            
            p Your will be charged <strong>$20.00</strong>.

            #payment-form

            .text-center
                button.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-primary(type='submit') Submit

